DataElement.preferredDefinition: A unique image identifier consisting of a sequence of letters, numbers, or other characters in the format of "IMAGE:N" where N is sequentially assigned by the tool generating an electronic file of Open Microscopy Environment (OME) tagged image file format (TIFF) data.
